snippet.title: CloserLookVR: Oldways - Announcement Trailer | Meta Quest
snippet.description:
CloserLookVR: Oldways is a story driven puzzle adventure game set in west Africa. Follow Tessy as she tries to find her way out of a locked down department.

Uncover an intriguing story of conspiracy and corruption. solve unique puzzles and find stolen artifacts.

Available soon
